snippet.textDisplay:
I do not know anyone who eats one slice of toast at a time. Half of a bagel? Or an 'english' muffin? I can understand the need and/or desire to up the game when it comes to making toast but $400.00 to cook one slice at a time is an extravagance I do not need nor want.
Mitsubishi execs must be sitting in their cubicles snickering when the sales reports come in.
Interesting video. Thanks for sharing!
